---
layout: base.njk
title: Everyone Deserves Housing
description: A proposed nonprofit model integrating shelter, healthcare, behavioral health, trauma-informed design, and housing pathways.
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="shell hero__grid">
    <div class="hero__content">
      <p class="eyebrow">{{ home.hero.eyebrow }}</p>
      <h1>{{ home.hero.title }}</h1>
      <p class="hero__summary">{{ home.hero.summary }}</p>
      <div class="hero__actions">
        <a class="button button--primary" href="{{ home.hero.primaryCta.href }}">{{ home.hero.primaryCta.label }}</a>
        <a class="button button--secondary" href="{{ home.hero.secondaryCta.href }}">{{ home.hero.secondaryCta.label }}</a>
      </div>
      <ul class="hero__highlights">
        {% for item in home.hero.highlights %}
          <li>{{ item }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="hero__visual">
      <figure class="polaroid">
        <img src="/docs-assets/cover-art.png" alt="Mural that reads Everyone Deserves Housing." loading="eager">
        <figcaption class="polaroid__caption">
          <span class="polaroid__line polaroid__line--top">Grounded in place.</span>
          <span class="polaroid__line polaroid__line--bottom">A local, human-first vision for shelter and care.</span>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--intro" id="mission">
  <div class="shell intro-panel">
    <div class="intro-panel__copy">
      <p class="section-label">Mission</p>
      <h2>{{ home.mission }}</h2>
      <p>This nonprofit is designed for street-level homelessness: immediate help, integrated care, and a clearer path forward.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="quick-facts">
      <article class="quick-fact">
        <div class="quick-fact__icon quick-fact__icon--green">
          <img src="/docs-assets/guiding-principles-checkmark.svg" alt="" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <span>24/7</span>
        <p>Front-door access and stabilization</p>
      </article>
      <article class="quick-fact">
        <div class="quick-fact__icon quick-fact__icon--orange">
          <img src="/docs-assets/guiding-principles-house.svg" alt="" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <span>3+</span>
        <p>Specialized care paths designed into the shelter model</p>
      </article>
      <article class="quick-fact">
        <div class="quick-fact__icon quick-fact__icon--blue">
          <img src="/docs-assets/guiding-principles-handshake.svg" alt="" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <span>1</span>
        <p>Coordinated system from outreach to housing placement</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--light">
  <div class="shell">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <p class="section-label">Why this matters</p>
        <h2>The current path is too fragmented.</h2>
      </div>
      <p>People need care, connection, and safe places to stabilize. Too often they are asked to navigate disconnected services while in crisis.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="reason-grid">
      {% for item in home.rationale %}
        <article class="reason-card">
          <p>{{ item }}</p>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="model">
  <div class="shell feature-layout">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">How it works</p>
      <h2>One model. Several kinds of support.</h2>
      <p class="section-copy">Instead of separating shelter, healthcare, recovery support, and housing planning, the model brings them together and keeps people moving toward the right next step.</p>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        {% for item in home.programElements %}
          <article class="feature-card">
            <h3>{{ item.title }}</h3>
            <p>{{ item.text }}</p>
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <aside class="image-stack">
      <figure class="image-card image-card--large">
        <img src="/docs-assets/services-hill-scene.svg" alt="Illustration representing support services." loading="lazy">
      </figure>
      <div class="icon-ribbon">
        <div class="icon-ribbon__tile">
          <img class="icon-tone icon-tone--blue" src="/docs-assets/services-stethoscope.svg" alt="" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <div class="icon-ribbon__tile">
          <img class="icon-tone icon-tone--orange" src="/docs-assets/services-first-aid-kit.svg" alt="" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <div class="icon-ribbon__tile">
          <img class="icon-tone icon-tone--green" src="/docs-assets/services-handshake.svg" alt="" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--dark" id="workflow">
  <div class="shell workflow-layout workflow-layout--pathways">
    <div class="workflow-copy workflow-copy--pathways" style="max-width:50rem;">
      <p class="section-label">Pathways</p>
      <h2 style="max-width:100%">One hub. Tailored services.</h2>
      <p class="section-copy section-copy--light">{{ home.pathways.intro }}</p>
    </div>
    <article class="timeline__item timeline__item--hub timeline__item--hub-band">
      <p class="pathway-kicker">Shared entry point</p>
      <h3>{{ home.pathways.hub.title }}</h3>
      <p>{{ home.pathways.hub.text }}</p>
    </article>
    <div class="workflow-detail-grid">
      <aside class="workflow-visuals workflow-visuals--diagram">
        <figure class="image-card image-card--tone-white workflow-figure">
          <div class="workflow-figure__inner">
            <img src="/docs-assets/Pathways.png" alt="Diagram showing a stabilization hub with triage branching to medical respite, addiction recovery, low barrier, senior supportive, and rapid rehousing." loading="lazy">
          </div>
        </figure>
      </aside>
      <div class="workflow-copy workflow-copy--list">
      <ul class="pathway-list">
        {% for item in home.pathways.services %}
          <li class="pathway-list__item">
            <span class="pathway-list__label">{{ item.title }}</span>
            <span class="pathway-list__meta">{{ item.kind }}</span>
            <p>{{ item.text }}</p>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="shell values-layout">
    <div class="values-copy">
      <p class="section-label">What it should feel like</p>
      <h2>Safe, grounded, and built for real life.</h2>
      <p class="section-copy">Trauma-informed design is not decoration. The physical environment can either add stress or support healing, regulation, and trust.</p>
      <div class="mini-card-list">
        {% for item in home.designPrinciples %}
          <article class="mini-card">
            <h3>{{ item.title }}</h3>
            <p>{{ item.text }}</p>
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="principles-panel">
      <div class="values-visual">
        <figure class="image-card image-card--tone-white values-visual__tile">
          <img src="/docs-assets/guiding-principles-scales-of-justice.svg" alt="Illustration representing fairness and justice." loading="lazy">
        </figure>
        <figure class="image-card image-card--tone-white values-visual__tile">
          <img src="/docs-assets/guiding-principles-location-marker.svg" alt="Illustration representing local connection." loading="lazy">
        </figure>
        <figure class="image-card image-card--tone-white values-visual__tile">
          <img src="/docs-assets/guiding-principles-bar-chart.svg" alt="Illustration representing measurable outcomes." loading="lazy">
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class="principles-grid">
        {% for item in home.guidingPrinciples %}
          <article class="principle-chip">
            <h3>{{ item.title }}</h3>
            <p>{{ item.text }}</p>
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--light" id="partners">
  <div class="shell impact-layout">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Partners</p>
      <h2>Built with healthcare, behavioral health, and community partners.</h2>
      <ul class="pill-list">
        {% for item in home.partnerships %}
          <li>{{ item }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="impact-panel">
      <div class="impact-panel__brand">
        <img src="/docs-assets/logo.png" alt="Everyone Deserves Housing logo" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <p class="section-label">What success looks like</p>
      <ul class="stack-list">
        {% for item in home.outcomes %}
          <li>{{ item }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
      <div class="next-steps">
        <p class="section-label">Startup plan</p>
        <ol>
          {% for item in home.startupPlan %}
            <li>{{ item }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-card">
        <p class="section-label">{{ home.contact.label }}</p>
        <a class="contact-card__link" href="mailto:{{ home.contact.email }}">
          <img class="contact-card__icon" src="/docs-assets/email.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
          <span>{{ home.contact.email }}</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
